data.description: Pack your bags because this is the one! Built in 2009, this stunning 3 bed / 2 bath stepless ranch home is ideally situated on a serene cul-de-sac. As you enter, the open floor plan welcomes you with a flood of natural light, creating a bright and airy living space. The fireside living room, adorned with vaulted ceilings, seamlessly connects to the dining room, providing an ideal setting for hosting gatherings with family and friends. The elegant kitchen is adorned with brand new tile floors, an island, stainless steel appliances, and a charming breakfast area. The primary bedroom, featuring trey ceilings and a generously sized walk-in closet, offers a spacious retreat. The primary ensuite is equipped with a double vanity, soaking tub, and a separate shower. Upstairs, a large bonus room serves as an excellent space for an office or a kids' play area. Step outside to the brand new back deck, offering a picturesque view of the wooded backyard - the ideal spot for morning coffee or evening relaxation. Community amenities, including a pool and a playground, enhance the overall living experience. Conveniently located just minutes away from the vibrant downtown Douglasville and I-20, commuting is a breeze. Seize the opportunity to claim this beautiful ranch home as your own and enjoy the perfect blend of comfort and style!
